data.description: Open House today Saturday Feb. 24th from 1-4pm!!! Welcome to your dream home at River Rock Ranch! This residence epitomizes luxury living with a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. The fabulous gourmet kitchen caters to foodies and entertainers, offering a spacious layout and high-end appliances for memorable gatherings. The expansive gameroom provides a hub for family fun and relaxation, complemented by spacious bedrooms and 4 full baths for the ideal balance of privacy and togetherness. This Monticello home extends beyond your home with a fantastic amenity center featuring a winding river pool, covered playground, and a state-of-the-art fitness center. Enjoy a low tax rate and close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment in this gated community, ensuring security and tranquility. Don't miss the chance to own a Monticello home - a perfect blend of sophistication, comfort, and convenience in your forever home!
